/netflix-clone
│
├── index.html              → Main landing page (Netflix homepage)
├── browse.html             → Page with movie rows (after login)
├── login.html              → Login form (optional)
├── signup.html             → Sign-up form (optional)
├── movie.html              → (Optional) Single movie details popup/page
│
├── /css
│   └── style.css           → All styles
│
├── /js
│   └── script.js           → All JavaScript logic
│
├── /images
│   ├── logo.png
│   ├── banner.jpg
│   └── thumbnails/
│       └── movie1.jpg
│
├── /videos                 → (Optional) Movie trailers
│   └── trailer1.mp4
│
├── /assets                 → Fonts, icons, etc.
│   └── NetflixSans.ttf
│
├── README.md               → Project description (for GitHub)
└── .gitignore              → (optional) GitHub-related








Start → index.html
         ↓
   [Login / Sign Up]
   ↓         ↓
login.html   signup.html
     ↓
browse.html
     ↓
(Optional) movie.html (when clicking on a movie poster)
